    "\n",
    "To study the instability that connects the metastable Q-ball to the true vacuum we need the Q-cloud configuration with the **same** charge.  Rather than scanning in frequency from scratch, we use the cached scan produced by `build_qcloud_profile_for_charge`, which looks up (or generates) a table of $\\omega$ values and interpolates the one that reproduces $g^2 Q_{\\text{target}}$.\n"
