    "## Unstable Eigenmode around the Q-cloud\n",
    "\n",
    "The Q-cloud hosts a single negative mode that mediates the decay towards the true vacuum.  We compute this mode by linearising around the Q-cloud profile and solving the radial eigenvalue problem.  The resulting growth rate $\\gamma$ also fixes the natural Euclidean time scale used later in the full two-dimensional bounce.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
